  "prompt": "How much did each actor get paid to star in The Avengers?",
  "response": "The salaries of actors for \"The Avengers\" (2012) varied widely. Here are some estimates based on public reports:\n\n- **Robert Downey Jr.**: Around $50 million, which includes his base salary and backend profits.\n- **Chris Evans**: Approximately $6-7 million.\n- **Chris Hemsworth**: Around $5 million.\n- **Scarlett Johansson**: Estimated at around $6-7 million.\n- **Jeremy Renner**: Approximately $3-4 million.\n- **Mark Ruffalo**: Estimated at around $2-3 million.\n- **Tom Hiddleston**: Roughly around $2-3 million.\n- **Samuel L. Jackson**: Around $4-6 million.\n\nNote that these figures include base salaries as well as potential bonuses and backend earnings. Exact amounts can vary depending on sources and updates.",
